org.dellroad.jibxbindings.pidf.lo

Class CAValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dellroad.jibxbindings.pidf.lo.CAValue

  • public class CAValue
extends Object
    One field in a <ca:civicAddress> element as defined in RFC 5139. This differs from LangContent in that the field content is whitespace normalized.
